title: Jerry Garcia 07/08/79
description:
An incredible and rare show! 

 Reconstruction featuring Jerry Garcia Live at the Keystone in Berkeley, CA 07/08/79


 Source: Master Soundboard Reels (7" @ 7.5ips) > 2 PCM > DAT > CD

  
  For those of you who know what it is, this is a Betty Board Show.  It is an amazing recording straight to digital from the original reel-to-reel.

 CD #1
1. Make It Better
2. Someday Baby
3. Soul Roach
4. What You Won't Do For Love
5. Lyinda
6. It's No Use

CD #2
1. Tellin' My Friends
2. The Jealous Kind
3. That's What Love Will Make You Do
4. Fast Tone
5. Dear Prudence


p.s.  If you don't know of the Betty Board recordings it's worth Googeling.
